---
import Base from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<Base title="About — Deen & Dopamine" current="/about">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-300">I'm Athar Aalam — a Psychology student exploring how Qur’an & Sunnah meet cognitive science. This project is for Muslims who want grounded, practical mental health tools without pseudo-spiritual fluff.</p>
    <ul class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <li class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/60 ring-1 ring-white/10">Evidence-based, Sunnah-aligned</li>
      <li class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/60 ring-1 ring-white/10">Simple language, actionable steps</li>
      <li class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/60 ring-1 ring-white/10">Gen-Z friendly, no cringe</li>
      <li class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/60 ring-1 ring-white/10">No cult vibes, no gatekeeping</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
